title._content: Ernst Family at Horst Hop Ranch, 1946

description._content: Original Collection: Extension and Experiment Station Communications Item Number: P120:2573 Item Description: Frank Ernst, second left, and wife, fourth left, with their family working on the Horst Hop Ranch near Independence. He is a carpenter; she is a nurse; they are vacationing. Kids are Johnny, 11 left; Alice Marie, 16, light shirt; Mary Ann, 13, fifth from left; twins Lue and Sue, 15: and Paul, 9, foreground right.
